@DATABASE "Game Over II"
@NODE "MAIN" "SPECCY POKES - G - Game Over II"
@TOC "MAIN"

                   ZX SPECTRUM (SPECCY heheh) POKES - G
                   ====================================

                            Game Over II Part 2
                            ===================


DESCRIPTION              POKE
===========              ====

@{"Infinite Lives" RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(57743,0)"}          57743,0
@{"Skip Password " RXS "ADDRESS COMMAND ZXAMPoke(64559,201)"}          64559,201

                         I hacked this one since EVERYONE seemed to have
                         printed the same wrong POKE from YS!

                         I also left my "Skip Password" POKE here, as I
                         found the copy on Speccy Sensations 2 is saved
                         at the password stage! Just activate the POKE
                         before running the game, and it should jump 
                         straight to the menu.

                         Rastan
@endnode
